snippet.title: Mad Paradox gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Mad Paradox, Dos PC game produced by Queen Soft in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/mad-paradox/1483/
Playing this RPG with spicy images in it. At the age of 17 you're discovering the true story of the death of your parents. And decide revenge..
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
